main event: An individual filled out a UFO report for Project Blue Book in 1959 regarding an unidentified object.
interesting points: The individual could not estimate the speed of the object, but believed it was perhaps as far as a thousand yards away, The individual provided personal details including name, address, occupation, age, and educational background, The report indicates the individual is a male aged 28, The job title given is US N4R (Naus) Supervisor at a plant, The questionnaire was completed on 2 September 1959.
witness description: individual with educational background up to post graduate
